headline: MGM Resorts (MGM) Stock Trades Down, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of hospitality and casino entertainment company MGM Resorts (NYSE:MGM) fell 3.2% in the afternoon session after analysts lowered their price targets, citing concerns about weaker-than-expected growth in Las Vegas.
